{"tid":1628933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係分化撚，入黎屌我","createTime":"2019-10-06T05:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:50:42.000Z","uid":312979,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80b9bf7f6e7c7e2abbe2078b2c826af9a9504907","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"我屌曬你地班人，仲記唔記得咩叫<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山各自努力</span>？<br />\n想出港島就港島，九龍就九龍，最緊要識得plan 定條後路走<br />\n至於裝修個邊，搞中資真係冇所為，我贊成！<br />\n但手足們記得要諗番破壞完之後點樣防止有心人入店偷野，我地要記得幫人地裝修個原意係咩！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成個連登都有好多有心人帶風向，希望手足們可以用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span></span>去判斷做定唔做！<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad161adc22640e1f2b74c893284fc9aff75d9109","tid":1628933,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7acec4f88c7e9213245cc2e57470348652be612b","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ab2444704e9a17150907f7a4c9e50064f7c8522f","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7a33651ac38cf147f0868593f164f1d912563491","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a34d3a7fd50326d74b668e6c0f1cf34544454f75","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"29c27a1b80075efa12b6e2382a0c953ef9da0c42","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"30c1dc28fb5d22d1274c980c67e2dfc42d8cf8db","tid":1628933,"uid":312979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:36